				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-V%C4%83n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/An-Ho%E1%BA%A1ch-s%C6%A1n-B%C3%A1o-%C3%82n-t%E1%BB%B1-bi-k%C3%BD/poem-VMsZJa3_qA9RQB4PwzHmIQ">An Hoạch sơn Báo Ân tự bi ký - 安獲山報恩寺碑記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-V%C4%83n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-PPHKNipjENvZFLSGPiZIhQ">Chu Văn Thường</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BA%A1ch-Thu%E1%BB%B7-huy%E1%BB%87n-Th%C3%B4i-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7-th%E1%BA%ADp-c%E1%BB%ADu-%C3%B4ng-cao-trai-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-jee9SU4z1mg8j-OgwK2PPA">Bạch Thuỷ huyện Thôi thiếu phủ thập cửu ông cao trai tam thập vận - 白水縣崔少府十九翁高齋三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng/B%E1%BA%AFc-m%C3%B4n-to%E1%BA%A3-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c/poem-sQ61b_tRE4rLSVWs7Gju4g">Bắc môn toả thược - 北門鎖鑰</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng/author-5a-Wq7efQfwZ4d03tMrwxg">Phạm Đình Trọng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/Canh-T%C3%BD-nh%E1%BB%8B-nguy%E1%BB%87t-bi%E1%BB%87t-ch%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-ipI2vJqDdzs5TGkIKYQPHw">Canh Tý nhị nguyệt biệt chư đệ kỳ 1 - 庚子二月別諸弟其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/Gi%E1%BB%9Bi-l%E1%BB%99-h%C3%A0nh/poem-X27K1iiWEE3mGDA6ZHAXrw">Giới lộ hành - 薤露行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/author-eKAWfrr_7bNBR5FBbe19qg">Tào Tháo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/H%E1%BA%A1-quy-Lam-S%C6%A1n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-ZIJt7JaVyf416-7LPxCNHw">Hạ quy Lam Sơn kỳ 1 - 賀歸藍山其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-V%C4%83n-Ngh%E1%BB%8B-I/Qu%C3%A1-Kinh-Thanh-%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu-c%E1%BB%95/poem-wnGigdDlDNAkawVquX0lig">Quá Kinh Thanh điếu cổ - 過涇清吊古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-V%C4%83n-Ngh%E1%BB%8B-I/author-j2yv60iLSGVWsUs_D51NxQ">Phạm Văn Nghị (I)</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1/T%E1%BA%B7ng-V%C3%B5ng-La-nh%C3%A2n/poem-x6R68mFUlgInVpVW7sXECA">Tặng Võng La nhân - 贈網羅人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1/author-AqEVkg0YBflkFbuAXYlrbA">Hoàng Nguyễn Thự</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-D%C6%B0/T%E1%BB%91i-%C3%A1i-Gia-Nguy%C3%AAn/poem-6hqm6mqZrlEH4sgxNeDDFg">Tối ái Gia Nguyên - 最愛家元</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-D%C6%B0/author-jwIeMxg44qgv_V08xi02Hw">Trần Ngọc Dư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-I/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Th%E1%BA%A1ch-Qu%C3%BD-Lu%C3%A2n/poem-3KuAOocjSLU8sPKoUhrlNA">Vịnh Thạch Quý Luân - 詠石季倫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-I/author-HnN-F-u3X2ZCk1P9hm25HA">Lý Thanh (I)</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
